client.download

Class GameDownload

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • client.download.GameDownload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class GameDownload
extends java.lang.Thread
    GameDownload handles the download/extraction of a Game.

    Listens for the incoming game and saves to the gamepath of the user. After the download finished the game gets extracted and the downloaded file is deleted. The GameDownload tracks the progress of the download and extraction. The download or extraction can be stopped by calling stopDownloadUnzip().

    Since:
    1.0
